{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bbb003d508","title":"转发天津市通过各界人民代表扩大会议进行镇反工作的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d963469dc3","index":0,"year":1951,"month":4,"day":17,"articleId":"bbb003d508"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"7534c0b3f1","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"bbb003d508","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"天津市公安局1951年4月9日总结的通过召开各界人民代表扩大会议进行镇反的报告中说，天津市于3月27日召开第三届各界协商委员会第四次扩大会议讨论镇压反革命问题，之后又于29日召开1.5万人的市区各界人民代表扩大会议，揭发控诉反革命分子的罪行。大会实况由电台广播，组织了50万市民收听。会议进行了5个小时，到会群众情绪一直高涨，会后各界反映很好。"}],"contents":[{"id":"560d5b26ad","type":"title","text":"转发天津市通过各界人民代表扩大会议进行镇反工作的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"bbb003d508"},{"id":"7534c0b3f1","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，并转分局，省委，大中市委，区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"bbb003d508"},{"id":"bf63d633cb","type":"paragraph","text":"天津镇反工作做得很好，团结和教育了各界人民，一切地方均应照此办理，坚决地打破神秘主义和关门主义的作风。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"bbb003d508"},{"id":"130129d7ec","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"bbb003d508"},{"id":"ff473fd207","type":"paragraph","text":"四月十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"bbb003d508"}],"page":{"id":"42e60f980d","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"bbb003d508","start":239,"end":239}}}},"__N_SSG":true}